      "message": "[Major] Line 86: Appending /usr/lib/$(HOST)/pkgconfig and /usr/share/pkgconfig to PKG_CONFIG_PATH globally can make cross builds resolve host .pc files instead of contrib/sysroot packages. That breaks reproducibility and can silently link against incompatible host libraries. Keep host paths out of HAVE_CROSS_COMPILE builds, or derive them from the configured sysroot only.\n```suggestion\nifndef HAVE_CROSS_COMPILE\nPKG_CONFIG_PATH :\u003d $(PREFIX)/lib/pkgconfig:$(PREFIX)/lib/$(HOST)/pkgconfig:$(PKG_CONFIG_PATH):/usr/lib/$(HOST)/pkgconfig:/usr/share/pkgconfig\nelse\nPKG_CONFIG_PATH :\u003d $(PREFIX)/lib/pkgconfig:$(PREFIX)/lib/$(HOST)/pkgconfig:$(PKG_CONFIG_PATH)\nendif\n```",
