      "message": "[Major] Line 1852: bodyOverwritePreCachedMessages stores shared_ptrs while holding loadedHistory_.mutex, then dereferences and copies the pointed-to messages after releasing the lock. Other code can concurrently mutate pluginData/editions on the same SwarmMessage, so the copy passed to plugins is still racing. Store value snapshots plus ids while locked, and only write back resolved pluginData under the lock.\n```suggestion\nstd::vector\u003cstd::pair\u003cstd::string, libjami::SwarmMessage\u003e\u003e toOverwrite;\n{\n    std::lock_guard lk(loadedHistory_.mutex);\n    for (auto\u0026 [id, msg] : loadedHistory_.quickAccess) {\n        if (msg-\u003etype \u003d\u003d \"text/plain\" \u0026\u0026 needsWork)\n            toOverwrite.emplace_back(id, *msg);\n    }\n}\nfor (auto\u0026 [id, snapshot] : toOverwrite) {\n    std::vector single {snapshot};\n    pluginChatManager.transformSwarmMessages(single, accountId_, convId);\n    ...\n    std::lock_guard writeLk(loadedHistory_.mutex);\n    auto it \u003d loadedHistory_.quickAccess.find(id);\n    if (it \u003d\u003d loadedHistory_.quickAccess.end())\n        continue;\n    ...\n}\n```",
